{"tid":2056320,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"回到石器，我在發石器夢！","createTime":"2020-06-08T14:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T13:24:55.000Z","uid":116840,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec359b3e0cdb6af69f1abd6f3097886427ce6e7","tid":2056320,"uid":116840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/6dLbD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F6dLbD4.jpg&h=03955412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/njNbEH9FvEM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnjNbEH9FvEM&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19qnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=4470ed03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/njNbEH9FvEM</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次開服，興奮而且充滿幻想，經常問自己開服是為了什麼？沒資金，沒人手，沒經驗！<br />\n弟弟常跟我說，別想太多，想做就去做吧，我會全力支援你！這樣就開始了我們的石器夢，我追求最原始的味道，我不要韓國寵物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/GaZwF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FGaZwF6.jpg&h=1743eddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開服初期很痛苦，一直有找以前相熟的朋友，幫我做內部測試，他們眼中充滿懷疑，不用開口，我已經知道他們在想什麼，結果又是只剩下我跟弟弟，沒日沒夜的測試，修改，再測試！<br />\n過程十分痛苦，因為沒資金，我們付不起那高昂的客戶端費用，弟弟只好網上找到好幾個免費的客戶端，這幾個客戶端不是被種了後門，就是被惡意刪代碼，目的只有一個！就是要你放棄自己架構，轉聘他們當技術，一切都是套路！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/1VbMaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F1VbMaL.jpg&h=5b9b4b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n弟弟連續三個月，每天睡兩小時，早上回到自己公司處理事情，下班後，馬上跑回家，重新編寫整個客戶端，有人說這還不是SF嗎？還當自己做了新遊戲，事實上要重寫一個十幾年前的舊產物, 工程量是難以相像的! 因為人手有限, 沒辦法完整測試, 結果BUG多不行, 同行看不起, 勸我放棄, 我說BUG 嘛總有一天會修完的! 武林高手也不是第一天就會武功呀!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/Hn4yDt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FHn4yDt.png&h=661fcf1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同行抹黑, 恥笑, 攻擊, 翻賴群各種手段不斷發生!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/2P6AbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F2P6AbZ.png&h=25f3c0e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/hZHxzw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FhZHxzw.png&h=b1c83e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/F82Yrh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FF82Yrh.png&h=9e6868ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/vEQ3cF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FvEQ3cF.jpg&h=06dd4f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/q5rDVe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2Fq5rDVe.jpg&h=47505fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/jOlIcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FjOlIcS.jpg&h=f4999456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們一直堅持著, 一直在作石器夢!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWJEkkNM784&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaWJEkkNM784%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19qnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=d2b69fbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWJEkkNM784&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n終於我們達成了千人上線!!!! <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/9dHA0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F9dHA0M.jpg&h=2e065214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/kYfCo0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FkYfCo0.jpg&h=87f799ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/3n5txj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F3n5txj.jpg&h=d3fb408b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/psoH1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FpsoH1R.jpg&h=8dcc4b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/xSlmdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FxSlmdX.jpg&h=566df58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/0BnrmU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2F0BnrmU.jpg&h=9f31d6f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/Peqmzc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FPeqmzc.jpg&h=9dc3a1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/sBeoqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FsBeoqY.jpg&h=735c02a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/xDYLZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FxDYLZT.jpg&h=66137043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/j0oQsD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2Fj0oQsD.jpg&h=d562578d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/06/08/Aa6MSv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2FAa6MSv.jpg&h=5d73e1dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們的石器夢還在繼續! 你願意陪我們一齊作夢嗎!!?<br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://www.returnsa.com\" data-sr-url=